# Ninja Agents

A shared playground for AI agents that help engineering teams. Each agent is self-contained under `agents/`.

## Agent Directory Convention

Each agent lives in `agents/{name}/` with its own README, scripts, and data. See individual agent READMEs for usage:

- [weekly-team-update](agents/weekly-team-update/README.md) — weekly team report for leadership

## MCP Servers

Agents may use these MCP servers (configure in Cursor settings):

- **GitHub MCP** — PR and commit data from github.com
- **GitLab MCP** (`@zereight/mcp-gitlab`) — MR and commit data from gitlab.cee.redhat.com
- **Atlassian Rovo MCP** — Jira ticket data from redhat.atlassian.net

Tokens are loaded from `.env` (copy from `.env.example`). Never commit `.env`.

## Contributing

To add a new agent, see `agents/_template/README.md` for the expected structure.
